data.description: Welcome to Shadow Valley, a thriving new neighborhood known for its charm. Step into this recently built home, completed in 2021, and be greeted by modern accents and a stunning neutral color scheme. Boasting four bedrooms, two bathrooms, and a two-car garage, this home offers ample space for your family's needs. The open concept kitchen seamlessly flows into the living room, creating a spacious and welcoming atmosphere. The kitchen is equipped with a convenient walk-in pantry and a sleek gas stove, catering to your culinary needs. The primary bedroom features an en suite bathroom and a walk-in closet, providing a private sanctuary for relaxation. The additional bedrooms are generously sized, ensuring comfort for family members or guests. A dedicated laundry room adds convenience to your daily routine. Step outside to the backyard and discover a covered extended patio, perfect for enjoying outdoor gatherings or simply unwinding after a long day. Enjoy the peace and tranquility of Shadow Valley, while still being within easy reach of amenities, schools, and recreational activities. Don't miss the opportunity to own this exceptional home!
